name: Kelp forest (temp) - Mixed or rocky bottom with dense kelp algae - ecosystem component from the WIO Symphony tool
description: Kelp forests were mapped by combining available kelp polygons in the sanbi databas with a global suitability model on kelp distribution. The global model was adjusted to represent the lower likelyhood of kelp occurance compared with the mapped kelp beds. Known limitations: Metadata missing
